# Quick Commands
  - `godot .`  Run the game
  - `godot --headless -s tests/run_tests.gd`  Run tests

# Project Structure
  - `scenes/`   PackedScene assets (units, buildings, projectiles)
  - `scripts/`  Gameplay logic (Main, Economy, Placement, UI)
  - `data/`     Campaign level JSON files
  - `tests/`    GDScript test runner

